<!-- 
	orderInCategory - this will determine the order in which the items will be displayed in the dropdown menu
	showAsAction - this will determine how the item will be displayed
				never - will always be displayed in the dropdown menu
				always - will always display the item in the main action bar
				ifRoom - will display the item in the main action bar only if there is space, else it will be 
						displayed in the dropdown menu

 -->